baseline.description: Pass protocol proposals directly to execution checks without repair.
baseline.name: no_validation

suite.description: Plausible protocol envelopes with low-rate injected violations.
suite.injection_method: Violations are injected independently per protocol with Bernoulli(p), then sampled uniformly from {source_depletion, destination_overflow, thermal_limit}.
suite.name: realistic

violation_definition: A protocol is counted as violating when OpenAtoms dry_run raises a PhysicsError.
